metadata.name: #2 Alphabet
metadata.description:
The Hidden and Lightened Series is a collection of five twisty destinations, each with their own hidden theme. Hand drawn by me in 2015 in a period of two manic months, this collection is drawn with archival ink on 20" x 30" cold and hot pressed paper, then digitally colored in 2022 for my NFT journey. 6000x8400

#1     21 Hearts
#2    Alphabet
#3    Toys 
#4    Flowers
#5    Eyes
